  "texts": [
    "The left column shows the behavior of (a) f and (d) df /dx at the transition between the Z - q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM and the Z2 NM phases.",
    "The middle column, (b) and (e), displays the corresponding behavior for the transition between the Z ± q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM phases at low J2/J1 = 0.505.",
    "The right column illustrates (c) f and (f) df /dx across the low-T transitions at J2/J1 = 0.5, specifically the Z + q FM (T /J1 = 0.03) and QLRO (T /J1 = 0.06) phases into the Z + q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM phase.",
    "In the (a) and (b), the blue arrows indicate the non-analytic kink in f. (g) The behavior of cos(qΘ), see text, across the Z + q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM ↔ Z - q AFM ⊕ Z2 NM transitions for three different values of J2/J1.",
    "For J2/J1 = 0.51, the horizontal axis is T /J1 = 0.13085 + ∆(T /J1); for J2/J1 = 0.52, it is T /J1 = 0.1542+∆(T /J1); and for J2/J1 = 0.525, it is T /J1 = 0.1636 + ∆(T /J1)."
